window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A portal back to Earth. Disappearing AI. The final battle has begun.</p> <p>After living inside a video game for months, Clay now has the rare chance to log out. The only problem is: the game's AI guardians have run off to Earth themselves. The fate of all reality now hangs in the balance.</p> <p>With new powers and a new mission, Clay and his pals have three days to trek across post-apocalyptic Earth and recapture the runaway AI guardians. If they fail, both worlds online and off will cease to exist.</p> <p>Are you ready to log out?</p>"; 
